birth_date`, `preferred_gender`, `is_complete`, `created_at`, `updated_at`\n\nWa
it, but the PRD explicitly says `avatar_url` should be in `user_profiles`. And t
he generated `ProfileResponse` has `avatar_url`. If the actual DB doesn\'t have 
