ange_min/max). This entity is actually closer to the truth.\n\nI think the right
thing to do is:\n1. Update `database/entities/user-profile.entity.ts` to add `av
atar_url` and `photo_urls` \n2. Create a migration to add these columns to the D
B\n3. Fix the auth module to use the correct entity from `database/entities/`\n4
. Or, fix the auth module\'s entity and have both modules use the same entity\n\
nActually, the simplest and most correct approach:\n1. Create a migration `AddAv
atarUrlAndPhotoUrlsToUserProfiles` to add the missing columns\n2. Update `apps/a
pi/src/database/entities/user-profile.entity.ts` to include `avatar_url` and `ph
oto_urls`\n3. Fix `apps/api/src/modules/auth/auth.module.ts` to use the entity f
