lementing the profile feature systematically. Given the complexity, I\'ll use su
bagents where appropriate to parallelize work, but since many pieces depend on e
ach other, I\'ll do a lot directly.\n\nLet me plan the implementation:\n\n1. **B
ackend - Auth Module Fix**: Export TypeOrmModule so ProfileModule can reuse enti
ties\n2. **Backend - Profile Module**: Create profile controller, service, DTOs\
n3. **Backend - Photo Module**: Create photo controller, service, DTOs  \n4. **B
ackend - OSS Module**: Create OSS presigned URL controller and service\n5. **Bac
kend - ProfileCompletionGuard**: Guard that checks is_complete\n6. **Backend - A
ppModule**: Register new modules\n7. **Backend - API Contract**: Update profile.
yaml\n8. **Mobile - Profile Repository**: Abstract and implementation\n9. **Mobi
le - Profile BLoC**: States, events, bloc\n10. **Mobile - Profile Setup Page**: 
