at the auth entity:\n```typescript\n@Column("int", { nullable: true, name: "pref
erred_min_age" })\npreferredMinAge: number | null;\n\n@Column("int", { nullable:
true, name: "preferred_max_age" })\npreferredMaxAge: number | null;\n```\n\nAnd 
