age_min` / `preferred_age_max` in DTOs. The existing contract uses `age_range_mi
n` / `age_range_max`.\n\nI think the safest approach is:\n1. Update the API cont
ract to use `preferred_age_min` and `preferred_age_max` to match the plan and PR
