ofile\n\nThere's a URL mismatch. The existing contract and generated code use `/
api/v1/profile`, not `/api/v1/users/me/profile`.\n\nGiven that:\n1. The generate
d mobile models already exist and use `/api/v1/profile`\n2. The shared-types alr
eady generated code based on this contract\n3. Changing the URL would require re
